'''伍德布法羅地區自治市'''（{{lang-en|Regional Municipality of Wood Buffalo}}）是[[加拿大|加拿大]][[亞伯達省|亞伯達省]]東北部一個特別自治市（{{lang|en|specialized municipality}}），於1995年4月1日由[[麥克默里堡|麥克默里堡]]市和第143號改善區（{{lang|en|Improvement District No. 143}}）合併而成<ref name=woodbuffalo>{{cite web | url=http://www.municipalaffairs.alberta.ca/cfml/pdf_search/pdf/SMUN/0508/Regional_Municipality_of_Wood_Buffalo_OC_817_94_1995_No7.pdf | publisher=Province of Alberta | title=Order in Council (O.C.) 817/94 | date=December 21, 1994 | accessdate=August 1, 2010 | archive-date=2012-07-04 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68uIpONT5?url=http://www.municipalaffairs.alberta.ca/cfml/pdf_search/pdf/SMUN/0508/Regional_Municipality_of_Wood_Buffalo_OC_817_94_1995_No7.pdf }}</ref>，為亞省面積第二大的行政區劃，僅次於[[馬更些縣|馬更些縣]]<ref name=2006CSDs>{{cite web | url=http://www12.statcan.gc.ca/census-recensement/2006/dp-pd/hlt/97-550/Index.cfm?TPL=P1C&Page=RETR&LANG=Eng&T=301&SR=1&S=9&O=D | title=Population and dwelling counts, for Canada and census subdivisions (municipalities), 2006 and 2001 censuses - 100% data | publisher=Statistics Canada | date=January 6, 2010 | accessdate=October 3, 2011 | archive-date=2018-02-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180220212806/http://www12.statcan.gc.ca/census-recensement/2006/dp-pd/hlt/97-550/Index.cfm?TPL=P1C&Page=RETR&LANG=Eng&T=301&SR=1&S=9&O=D }}</ref>。伍德布法羅境内蘊藏[[油砂|油砂]]，近年能源業發展蓬勃，令其成為加拿大發展速度最快的工業地區之一。

==歷史==
為了更有效服務[[麥克默里堡|麥克默里堡]]及其周邊郊野地帶，亞伯達省政府於1995年4月1日將原有的麥克默里堡市和第143號改善區合併，成為伍德布法羅自治市（{{lang|en|Municipality of Wood Buffalo}}），為亞省首座特別自治市<ref name=woodbuffalo/>。合併後的麥克默里堡改設為城市服務區（{{lang|en|urban service area}}），地位據亞省的《市鎮政府法案》與市級行政區相若；伍德布法羅餘下範圍則設為郊野服務區（{{lang|en|rural service area}}），地位據《市鎮政府法案》與自治區相若<ref name=woodbuffalo/>。此行政區劃於1996年8月14日正式改稱伍德布法羅地區自治市<ref name=SMprofiles>{{cite web | url=http://www.municipalaffairs.alberta.ca/cfml/MunicipalProfiles/basicReport/SMUN.PDF | publisher=Alberta Municipal Affairs | title=Municipal Profiles (Specialized Municipalities) | date=December 27, 2013 | accessdate=December 30, 2013 | archive-date=2012-07-04 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68uImCZqF?url=http://www.municipalaffairs.alberta.ca/cfml/MunicipalProfiles/basicReport/SMUN.PDF }}</ref>。

受[[2016年麥克默里堡森林大火|2016年麥克默里堡森林大火]]影響，麥克默里堡及鄰近地區於2016年5月3日進入强制疏散令，逾8萬名居民從該帶撤離<ref name="largestAB">{{cite web|last1=Parsons|first1=Paige|title=Thousands flee from Fort McMurray wildfire in the largest fire evacuation in Alberta's history|url=http://edmontonjournal.com/news/local-news/fort-mcmurray-wildfire-pushed-back-even-as-temperatures-climb|accessdate=May 3, 2016|agency=Edmonton Journal|publisher=Postmedia Network|date=May 3, 2016|archive-date=2016-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160510222635/http://edmontonjournal.com/news/local-news/fort-mcmurray-wildfire-pushed-back-even-as-temperatures-climb}}</ref><ref name="FMCCBC">{{cite web|title=Wildfire destroys Fort McMurray homes, most of city evacuated|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/fort-mcmurray-fire-social-media-reflects-fear-worry-as-the-flames-enter-city-1.3564982|accessdate=May 3, 2016|work=CBC News Edmonton|date=May 3, 2016|archive-date=2019-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190214175252/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/fort-mcmurray-fire-social-media-reflects-fear-worry-as-the-flames-enter-city-1.3564982}}</ref>，為亞省歷來最大規模的居民疏散行動<ref name="largestAB"/>。

