由伍德布法羅地區自治市政府進行的2015年人口普查顯示，境内總人口為125,032，當中常駐居民佔82,724，非常駐居民則佔42,308<ref name=2015MAPL>{{cite web | url=http://municipalaffairs.alberta.ca/documents/msb/2015_Municipal_Affairs_Population_List.pdf | title=2015 Municipal Affairs Population List | publisher=Alberta Municipal Affairs | isbn=978-1-4601-2630-1 | accessdate=February 23, 2016 | archive-date=2016-10-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161004185447/http://municipalaffairs.alberta.ca/documents/msb/2015_Municipal_Affairs_Population_List.pdf }}</ref>。由[[加拿大統計局|加拿大統計局]]進行的2011年人口普查則顯示，伍德布法羅境内人口則為65,565，較2006年的51,496人上升27.3%。以該行政區的{{convert|63637.47|km2|sqmi}}土地面積計算，當地2011年的人口密度為{{convert|1.0|/km2|/sqmi}}<ref name=2011censusABmunis>{{cite web | url=http://www12.statcan.gc.ca/census-recensement/2011/dp-pd/hlt-fst/pd-pl/Table-Tableau.cfm?LANG=Eng&T=302&SR=1&S=51&O=A&RPP=9999&PR=48&CMA=0 | title=Population and dwelling counts, for Canada, provinces and territories, and census subdivisions (municipalities), 2011 and 2006 censuses (Alberta) | publisher=Statistics Canada | date=February 8, 2012 | accessdate=February 8, 2012 | archive-date=2012-07-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120722143610/http://www12.statcan.gc.ca/census-recensement/2011/dp-pd/hlt-fst/pd-pl/Table-Tableau.cfm?LANG=Eng&T=302&SR=1&S=51&O=A&RPP=9999&PR=48&CMA=0 }}</ref>。

